instructions on how to run PopLDDecay:
to open manual and help, run the program ./PopLDdecay or the perl Plot_MultiPop.pl without any command.

run PopLDDecay for each of the population you would like to analyze. run by executing the following:

#usage:

	./PopLDdecay -InVCF Input_vcf.gz -OutStat output.stat

to plot:

	perl Plot_MultiPop.pl -inList List_of_LD_stats.txt -output OUT_prefix

for the list of LD stats, compile the path to the statistics in one file in the following format:

	~/path/to/file.output.pop1.stat.gz	pop1
	~/path/to/file.output.pop2.stat.gz	pop2
	~/path/to/file.output.pop3.stat.gz	pop3
	~/path/to/file.output.pop4.stat.gz	pop4

and save it in a text file.
